{"tid":2032903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我地目標就係俾國際睇政府打壓和平示威","createTime":"2020-05-24T10:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T13:18:37.000Z","uid":200087,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f9690da9a24c18494188939356664b7ac7ab05","tid":2032903,"uid":200087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:18:23.000Z","msg":"要打贏一個政權，尤其係香港呢個情況，我地需要嘅係手段、要比起中共更會用手段。<br />\n<br />\n經濟我地已經做到攬炒，下一步目標我地應該放係輿論方面，擴大、增加支持我地理念的人。<br />\n<br />\n爭取自由民主係一條漫長的路，係無可能短時間內成功。我地要比敵人更加理性，揸緊我地嘅宗旨，不斷反思自己有冇犯左一個強權會做嘅錯事。<br />\n<br />\n討論時要基於邏輯思維，不標籤，不人身攻擊，無時無刻注意自己有冇犯邏輯謬誤。我地只有不斷反思、進步，先可以成功。 <br />\n<br />\n感謝各位手足。"},{"pid":"f86bbc2154084ed8573877cd10e8a30556ededfa","tid":2032903,"uid":200087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:20:07.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce63aab2567555e242a6e7694c1241f98b36bc5","tid":2032903,"uid":200087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b0e45289cc4d541c985bede843c0d3f0e554bd","tid":2032903,"uid":200087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c66efdebc75e76f5c2627833d0bfef7c41465ce7","tid":2032903,"uid":200087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"獨立思考唔係得個講字"},{"pid":"a2e3435cff7db41eb84a02138bb672c15bcf19f7","tid":2032903,"uid":200087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35707550bd8de185978bb55a47ee00d75fc8efff","tid":2032903,"uid":200087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173b120f0def1dd17a74c4be96d1093ffbe313ba","tid":2032903,"u